	  b quest_dialog = true;
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "Welcome, traveler. Please, have a seat. May I offer you a cup of warm tea? Yes, travelling in this forest is harsh. But there are worse places to be, such as the village of Rothelio's Heart. Its very earth is being corrupted by a powerful necromancer. And this tragedy only yields other tragedies.\n\nNot too long ago, Adratah the elven high priest with his followers sought my help. They wished to seize control of the forest spectres. I haven't heard such a foul, foolish idea in a long time, so I sent them away. They barricaded themselves at the Sacred Grove, and are bending the poor creatures to their will. Traveller, buy any supplies you need from me, but I beg you, find Adratah and stop his misguided efforts. I have destroyed their barricades for you.";
